Subject: Make git-commit complete both modified files and git-added files.
Cc: "Nikolai Weibull" <now@bitwi.se>, "Clint Adams" <clint@zsh.org>
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
